      "text": "BUDKA, Philipp, Martin EBNER, Walther NAGLER und Claudia SCHALLERT, 2011. Hochschule - Strukturen, Rahmen und Modelle für die Lehre mit Technologien. Lehrbuch für Lernen und Lehren mit Technologien [online]. 28 Januar 2011. Nr. 0. [Zugriff am: 6 August 2021]. Verfügbar unter: https://l3t.tugraz.at/index.php/LehrbuchEbner10/article/view/58\n> **Abstract**. Based on the existing educational landscape and its politically historical development corset, this paper discusses the potential of teaching and learning at universities supported by digital media and technologies. With special consideration of organizational and infrastructural framework conditions and on the basis of the special case of university mass teaching, a didactic model and the applications of learning management systems are presented. The main focus is on the question of how interaction and interactivity in courses can be increased and improved by means of corresponding didactic models and with the support of learning systems. Examples from practice and measures for the use of digital media technologies in university teaching complete the chapter. \n"
